rong-tuan-qua-tet-tu-choi-nhung-xe-sang-thi-nhan-359905.html" /><meta property="og:image" content="http://imgs.vietnamnet.vn/Images/2017/03/06/15/20170306155526-20170228093913-anh-xe.jpg" /><meta name="news_keywords" content="Xe sang, doanh nghiệp, Đà Nẵng, Cà Mau, tặng quà Tết" /><link id="canonical" rel="canonical" href="http://vietnamnet.vn/vn/tuanvietnam/dachieu/an-tuong-trong-tuan-qua-tet-tu-choi-nhung-xe-sang-thi-nhan-359905.html" /><link rel="alternate" media="handheld" href="http://m.vietnamnet.vn/vn/tuanvietnam/dachieu/an-tuong-trong-tuan-qua-tet-tu-choi-nhung-xe-sang-thi-nhan-359905.html" /><script type="text/javascript">
